*Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-uːtə(r)|-uːtə(r)]]

===Noun===
'''tutor'''
#One who [[teaches]] another (usually a student, learner, or [[tutee]]) in a one-on-one or small-group interaction.
#:''He passed the difficult class with help from his '''tutor'''.''

===Verb===
'''tutor'''
#(transitive) To [[instruct]] or [[teach]], especially to an individual or small group.
#:''She [[tutored]] beginning engineering students in calculus and physics.

